w%20can%20you%20avoid%20being%20pulled%20into%20his%20drama%20against%20your%20will%3F%20Think%20through%20exactly%20how%20you%20are%20and%20aren't%20willing%20to%20be%20involved.%20For%20instance%2C%20you%20disagree%20with%20his%20choice%20to%20dodge%20child%20support.%20Tell%20him%20so%2C%20and%20explain%20why.%20You%20could%20say%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20understand%20that%20your%20ex%20hurt%20you%20deeply%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20finance%20her%20life.%20However%2C%20I%20love%20your%20kids%20very%20much%2C%20and%20they%20deserve%20your%20support.%20I%20won't%20participate%20in%20you%20finding%20a%20way%20to%20get%20out%20of%20caring%20for%20them%20financially.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollow%20this%20up%20with%20something%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20do.%20Maybe%20you%20can%20pick%20the%20kids%20up%20from%20his%20ex's%20place%20on%20the%20days%20he%20gets%20them%20so%20he%20doesn't%20have%20to%20see%20her.%20Or%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20any%20ugly%20pick-up%20and%20drop-off%20disputes%20like%20the%20ones%20that%20gave%20me%20shingles%2C%20you%20can%20offer%20to%20help%20him%20find%20an%20attorney%20to%20help%20him%20fight%20for%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20here%20is%20being%20intentional%20and%20insistent%20on%20your%20boundaries%20with%20your%20brother.%20His%20presence%20in%20your%20life%2C%20and%20therefore%20his%20problems%20in%20your%20life%2C%20are%20a%20foregone%20conclusion%2C%20but%20you%20get%20to%20choose%20how%20to%20interact%20with%20that%20presence%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20comfortable%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20you%20are%20worried%20about%20his%20ability%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20this%20divorce%20without%20you%20letting%20him%20live%20with%20you%2C%20but%20remember%20%E2%80%94%20toxic%20relationships%20tend%20to%20involve%20as%20many%20breakups%20as%20they%20do%20reconciliations.%20Whether%20you%20let%20him%20move%20in%20with%20you%20or%20not%20won't%20ch