e%20oil%20industry%20grievances%20over%20Biden's%20policies%2C%20the%20US%20has%20experienced%20record%20oil%20production%2C%20leading%20to%20substantial%20profits%20for%20major%20energy%20companies%20like%20ExxonMobil%20and%20Chevron%2C%20said%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Mar-a-Lago%20dinner%2C%20Trump%20promised%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeal%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20the%20oil%20giants%2C%20vowing%20to%20expedite%20permits%20for%20new%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20(LNG)%20exports%20and%20auction%20off%20more%20drilling%20leases%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%2C%20said%20The%20Post%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20in%20the%20industry%20initially%20favored%20alternative%20Republican%20contenders%2C%20Trump's%20steadfast%20commitment%20to%20pro-oil%20policies%20has%20garnered%20reluctant%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2024%2Fjan%2F18%2Ftrump-republican-rivals-climate-crisis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20%26quot%3Bdrill%2C%20baby%2C%20drill%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3Emantra%20and%20promises%20of%20deregulation%20continue%20to%20resonate%20within%20the%20oil%20patch%2C%20contrasting%20starkly%20with%20Biden's%20green-energy%20agenda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Trump%2C%20in%20a%20Fox%20News%20town%20hall%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20Iowa%20primary%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20more%20liquid%20gold%20under%20our%20feet%3B%20energy%2C%20oil%2C%20and%20gas%20than%20any%20other%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20clean%20energy%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20scam%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20execs%20are%20disillusioned%20by%20Biden's%20failure%20to%20defend%20their%20industry's%20interests%20despite%20spending%20%24400%20million%20to%20lobby%20the%20administration%20last%20year%2C%20the%20sources%20told%20the%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20campaign%20trail%20heats%20up%2C%20Trump's%20message%20to%20the%20oil%20industry%20