-821c-42f3-9678-ee6acfaf438f%5C%22%3E3.%20Sen.%20Marco%20Rubio%20of%20Florida%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERubio%20would%20be%20the%20most%20obvious%20choice%20for%20a%20Trump%20pick%20poised%20to%20carry%20the%20former%20president's%20legacy%20forward%20in%202028.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20Floridian%20was%20once%20proclaimed%20the%20future%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party.%20He%20did%20vote%20to%20certify%20the%202020%20election%20results%20but%20found%20ways%20other%20ways%20work%20with%20his%20former%202016%20primary%20rival%20while%20in%20office.%20Rubio%20has%20also%20shown%20he'll%20shift%20his%20views%2C%20most%20notably%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20main%20architects%20of%20the%20bipartisan%2C%20sweeping%202013%20immigration%20legislation%20that%20would%20have%20offered%20undocumented%20immigrants%20a%20pathway%20to%20citizenship.%20Like%20many%202016%20foes%2C%20Rubio%20is%20also%20on%20record%20hammering%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20including%20his%20cringey%20mocking%20of%20the%20future%20president's%20hand%20size%20(Rubio%20later%20apologized%20for%20that).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20hurdle%20for%20Rubio%20isn't%20likely%20anything%20in%20his%20past.%20Instead%2C%20he%20faces%20very%20real%20concerns%20about%20residing%20in%20the%20same%20state%20as%20Trump.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20Politifact%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politifact.com%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fmay%2F07%2Fa-donald-trump-marco-rubio-ticket-here-are-the-obs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexplained%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Constitution%20has%20been%20interpreted%20not%20to%20allow%20electors%20from%20the%20same%20state%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20president%20and%20vice%20president%20who%20also%20reside%20in%20that%20state.%20That%20means%20a%20Trump-Rubio%20ticket%20could%20lose%20out%20on%20Florida's%2030%20electoral%20votes%2C%20even%20if%20they%20won%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Bulwark%2C%20Rubio%20would