ection%20would%20be%20historic.%20She%20would%20be%20only%20the%20fourth%20woman%20to%20share%20a%20major%20party's%20ticket.%20Republicans%2C%20especially%20Trump%2C%20have%20struggled%20with%20suburban%20women%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20clear%20that%20tapping%20a%20woman%20would%20automatically%20cure%20that%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20may%20also%20delight%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20a%20House%20GOP%20leader.%20The%20president%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20attention%20to%20the%20drama%20that%20has%20gripped%20the%20lower%20chamber.%20Voters%20are%20likely%20to%20care%20more%20about%20the%20economy%20than%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson's%20job%20status%2C%20but%20the%20level%20of%20in-fighting%20in%20the%20GOP%20is%20so%20bad%20that%20multiple%20sitting%20lawmakers%20have%20quit%20their%20jobs%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22JD%20Vance%20walks%20through%20the%20Capitol%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e6b2cb4abc992e8c85ad4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20JD%20Vance%2C%20a%20Ohio%20Republican%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d482ef63-788f-4a20-bfdf-2b1fc5fcff95%5C%22%3E5.%20Sen.%20JD%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-donald-trump-jr-close-friendship-gop-america-first-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVance%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20used%20his%20powerful%20perch%20to%20push%20the%20GOP%20more%20in%20Trump's%20direction.%20He%20serves%20in%20a%20chamber%20that%2C%20unlike%20the%20House%2C%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20defy%20the%20former%20president.%20Despite%20just%20joining%20the%20Senate%20last%20year%2C%20the%2039-year-old%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20mentioned%20as%20a%20potential%20running%20mate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20former%20venture%20capitalist%2C%20Vance%20has%20ties%20to%20