EasyJet's%20flight%20attendants%20were%20friendlier%20than%20most%20I've%20encountered%20flying%20economy%20with%20legacy%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20budget%20carrier%20also%20seems%20to%20have%20the%20most%20respect%20for%20its%20customers%20because%20it%20doesn't%20have%20as%20many%20additional%20fees%20as%20Ryanair%20and%20Wizz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20took%20three%20flights%20in%20two%20days%20to%20compare%20Europe's%20three%20main%20budget%20airlines.%20They%20were%20all%20around%20two-and-a-half%20hours%20long.%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FICeN1%2F3%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20flights%20with%20Ryanair%2C%20Wizz%2C%20and%20easyJet%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22568%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20most%20impressed%20by%20easyJet%20thanks%20to%20its%20friendly%20flight%20attendants%2C%20and%20least%20liked%20Ryanair%20because%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20airline%20tries%20to%20squeeze%20out%20as%20much%20extra%20money%20as%20possible.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collage%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20Pete%20Syme%20taking%20selfies%20in%20front%20of%20an%20EasyJet%20Airbus%20A319%2C%20a%20Wizz%20Air%20A321neo%2C%20and%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633a6f610dfcda40965d5e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223508%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBooking%20the%20flights%2C%20easyJet%20was%20helpfully%20straightforward.%20There%20weren't%20any%20surprise%20pop-ups%20and%20every%20stage%20was%20clear.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222496%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20flight%20