ze%20this%20until%20I%20noticed%20the%20membership%20fee%20at%20checkout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWizz%20is%20also%20the%20only%20one%20of%20the%20three%20that%20doesn't%20take%20American%20Express%2C%20which%20can%20be%20disappointing%20if%20you%20want%20to%20maximize%20your%20rewards%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESince%20budget%20airlines%20have%20restrictive%20baggage%20rules%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20was%20a%20one-night%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20I%20only%20traveled%20with%20my%20trusty%20tartan%20rucksack.%20The%20night%20before%20my%20first%20flight%2C%20I%20checked%20its%20size%20against%20the%20airlines'%20limits.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rucksack%20with%20a%20tape%20measure%20laid%20on%20top%20of%20it%20measuring%2035cm%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6632441510dfcda409653928%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222827%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20bag's%20laid%20flat%2C%20it%20measured%20an%20inch%20or%20two%20wider%20than%20after%20I'd%20packed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEasyJet's%20app%20has%20a%20nifty%20augmented-reality%20tool%20which%20means%20you%20don't%20need%20a%20measuring%20tape%20for%20its%20size%20limit%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20largest%20of%20the%20three%20at%2045%20x%2036%20x%2020cm.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20from%20the%20easyJet%20app%20shows%20an%20augmented-reality%20box%20measuring%20the%20limits%20of%20a%20bag%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633b1760dfb1341e901c3a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EeasyJet%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20matched%20up%20at%20the%20airport's%20sizer.%20I%20couldn't%20find%20one%20for%20Wizz%2C%20but%20its%20limit%20is%20slightly%20smaller%20at%2040%20x%2030%20x%2