isting%20full%20statehood%20for%20Delhi%20as%20another%20guarantee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20he%20had%20run%20the%20promises%20past%20his%20partners%20in%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20the%20AAP%20leader%20said%20with%20folded%20hands%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20apologise%20for%20that.%20There%20is%20less%20time%2C%20the%20polls%20are%20halfway%20through.%20But%20I%20understand%20that%20they%20should%20not%20have%20any%20objection%20to%20opening%20schools%20and%20hospitals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20government%20is%20formed%2C%20I%20will%20get%20these%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20March%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20has%20been%20granted%20interim%20bail%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20let%20him%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20He%20has%20to%20surrender%20on%20June%202%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20last%20round%20of%20polling%20in%20the%20seven-phase%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715504700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmq7eog9o_arvind-kejriwal-ians_625x300_12_May_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-arvind-kejriwal-was-asked-if-he-may-be-india-blocs-pm-face-his-reply-5645694%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Asked%20if%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20AAP's%20INDIA%20allies%20before%20announcing%20%26quot%3Bguarantees%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20party%20has%20promised%20to%20fulfill%20if%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20wins%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20apologised%20to%20his%20allies%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-arvind-kejriwal-was-asked-if-he-may-be-india-blocs-pm-face-his-reply-5645694%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-arvind-kejriwal-was-asked-if-he-may-be-india-blocs-pm-face-his-reply-5645694%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-arvind-kejriwal-was-asked-if-he-may-be-india-blocs-pm-face-his-reply-5645694%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20%26quot%3B10%20Poll%20Guarantees%26quot%3B%20Include%20Giving%20Delhi%20Statehood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famanatullah-khan-in-arvind-kejriwals-meeting-with-aap-legislators-a-key-mla-missing-5645295%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20announced%20AAP's%20'10%20guarantees'%20if%20his%20party%20wins%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20assurances%20encompass%20a%20broad%20spectrum%20of%20public%20welfare%20initiatives%2C%20including%20pledges%20for%20free%20electricity%20and%20improved%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20has%20always%20failed%20on%20its%20promises%3B%20my%20guarantees%20have%20proven%20track%20record%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20to%20take%20a%20call%20whether%20to%20go%20for%20'Kejriwal%20ki%20Guarantee'%20or%20'Modi%20Guarantee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20forefront%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20electoral%20promises%20is%20the%20assurance%20of%20free%20electricity%20for%20all%2C%20particularly%20targeting%20the%20economically%20backward%20sections%20of%20society.%20The%20AAP%20chief%20advocated%20for%20replicating%20Delhi's%20model%20of%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply%20nationwide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOut%20of%20the%2010%20guarantees%2C%20the%20first%20guarantee%20is%20that%20we%20will%20provide%2024-hour%20electricity%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20country%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20generate%203%20lakh%20MW%20of%20electricity%20but%20the%20usage%20is%20only%202%20lakh%20MW.%20Our%20country%20can%20produce%20more%20electricity%20than%20the%20demand.%20We%20have%20done%20it%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20we%20will%20do%20it%20in%20the%20country%20also.%20We%20will%20provide%20up%20to%20200%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%20to%20all%20the%20poor.%20It%20will%20cost%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20crore%2C%20we%20can%20arrange%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%20on%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20poll%20guarantees%20list%20is%20revamping%20education%20in%20government%20schools.%20The%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20claimed%20that%20Rs%205%20lakh%20crore%20will%20be%20required%20to%20remedy%20that%20and%20that%20state%20governments%20and%20the%20Centre%20should%20pay%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20crore%20each%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20total%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20condition%20of%20our%20government%20schools%20is%20not%20good.%20Our%20second%20guarantee%20is%20that%20we%20will%20arrange%20good%20and%20excellent%20free%20education%20for%20everyone.%20Government%20schools%20will%20provide%20a%20better%20education%20than%20private%20schools.%20We%20have%20done%20it%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%20Rs%205%20lakh%20crore%20will%20be%20required%20for%20this.%20State%20governments%20will%20give%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20crore%20and%20central%20government%20will%20give%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20national%20convener%20also%20put%20a%20Rs%205%20lakh%20crore%20price%20tag%20to%20overhaul%20government%20hospitals%20and%20improve%20India's%20healthcare%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20condition%20of%20our%20government%20hospital%20is%20not%20good%20in%20our%20country.%20Our%20third%20guarantee%20is%20better%20healthcare.%20We%20will%20arrange%20good%20treatment%20for%20everyone.%20Mohalla%20clinics%20will%20be%20opened%20in%20every%20village%2C%20every%20locality.%20District%20hospital%20will%20be%20converted%20into%20a%20Multispeciality%20Hospital.%20Every%20person%20born%20in%20this%20country%20will%20get%20free%20treatment.%20Treatment%20will%20not%20be%20done%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20insurance%20as%20this%20is%20a%20big%20scam.%20We%20will%20create%20infrastructure.%20Rs%205%20lakh%20crore%20rupees%20will%20be%20spent%20on%20healthcare%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20guarantees%20on%20the%20list%2C%20according%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Bfreeing%26quot%3B%20Indian%20land%20from%20Chinese%20control%2C%20shutting%20down%20the%20Agniveer%20scheme%2C%20providing%20farmers%20MSP%20as%20per%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20report%20and%20a%20full%20statehood%20to%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20fourth%20guarantee%20is%20'Nation%20first'.%20China%20has%20occupied%20our%20land%20but%20our%20central%20govt%20is%20denying%20it...There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20strength%20in%20our%20army.%20All%20the%20land%20of%20the%20country%20which%20has%20been%20occupied%20by%20China%20will%20be%20freed.%20For%20this%2C%20efforts%20will%20be%20made%20at%20the%20diplomatic%20level%20on%20one%20side%20and%20the%20Army%20will%20be%20given%20complete%20freedom%20to%20take%20whatever%20steps%20it%20wants%20to%20take%20regarding%20this.%20A%20scheme%20like%20Agniveer%20is%20harmful%20for%20the%20army%20and%20the%20youth%20are%20also%20troubled%20by%20it.%20The%20Agniveer%20scheme%20will%20be%20withdrawn%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20probe%20agency%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20scam%20case%2C%20was%20granted%20interim%20bail%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20after%20leaving%20the%20Tihar%20jail%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20declared%20that%20the%20Opposition%20INDIA%20coalition%20would%20form%20the%20next%20government%2C%20with%20his%20AAP%20included%20in%20the%20alliance.%20The%20opposition%20coalition%2C%20comprising%20parties%20like%20AAP%2C%20Congress%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%2C%20and%20others%2C%20was%20established%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715503980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdu6hoa3g_arvind-kejriwal-_625x300_12_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-promises-free-electricity-healthcare-if-aap-wins-2024-polls-5645253%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%2010%20Guarantees%3A%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20unveiled%20AAP's%20'10%20guarantees'%20if%20his%20party%20wins%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-promises-free-electricity-healthcare-if-aap-wins-2024-polls-5645253%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-promises-free-electricity-healthcare-if-aap-wins-2024-polls-5645253%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-promises-free-electricity-healthcare-if-aap-wins-2024-polls-5645253%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranbir%20Kapoor%20takes%20it%20easy%20on%20Sunday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715503921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110052925%2Cimgsize-59314.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franbir-kapoor-takes-it-easy-on-sunday-amid-ramayana-legal-troubles%2Farticleshow%2F110052894.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C