erhood.%20Beyond%20the%20spotlight%2C%20Sushant's%20profound%20reflections%20unveil%20the%20essence%20of%20maternal%20love%20and%20the%20joy%20of%20nurturing%20young%20lives.%20Join%20us%20as%20we%20unravel%20Sushant's%20heartfelt%20insights%2C%20honoring%20the%20universal%20spirit%20of%20motherhood.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Meeting%20With%20AAP%20Legislators%2C%20A%20Key%20MLA%20Missing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20first%20meeting%20with%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20MLAs%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20him%20interim%20bail%20had%20a%20notable%20absence%20--%20Okhla%20MLA%20Amanatullah%20Khan.%20Mr%20Khan%20and%20his%20son%20Anas%20Ahmed%20are%20facing%20allegations%20of%20assaulting%20and%20threatening%20staff%20at%20a%20fuel%20pump%20in%20Noida%20Sector%2095.%20Cops%20have%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Khan%20and%20Anas%20are%20%26quot%3Bunderground%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20two%20under%20charges%20of%20assault%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20Noida%20police%20officers%20have%20said.%20The%20cops%20said%20a%20police%20team%20visited%20the%20MLA's%20residence%20to%20serve%20him%20a%20notice%2C%20but%20he%20was%20not%20found%20there.%20The%20officers%20have%20said%20Khan%20and%20his%20son%20were%20not%20cooperating%20in%20the%20investigation.%20Their%20phones%20are%20also%20switched%20off%2C%20according%20to%20the%20officers%20in%20Noida%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%2C%20police%20said%2C%20was%20registered%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20a%20fuel%20pump%20employee.%20The%20complainant%20has%20alleged%20that%20Anas%20visited%20the%20pump%20to%20refuel%20but%20jumped%20the%20queue.%20Anas%20was%20mentioned%20as%20%26quot%3Bunidentified%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20FIR.%20He%20allegedly%20insisted%20that%20his%20car%20should%20be%20refuelled%20first%20and%20assaulted%20the%20salesperson.%20Senior%20police%20officer%20Manish%20Kumar%20Mishra%20said%20the%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20at%20Phase%201%20police%20station%20against%20Mr%20Khan%2C%20Anas%20and%20some%20unidentified%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20MLA%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20his%20son%2C%20a%20student%20of%20law%2C%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20take%20an%20exam%20when%20the%20incident%20happened.%20%26quot%3BThe%20staff%20of%20the%20petrol%20pump%20misbehaved%20with%20my%20son%20and%20also%20manhandled%20him.%20Now%2C%20they%20are%20using%20incomplete%20CCTV%20footage%20to%20malign%20my%20image%20and%20frame%20me%20in%20a%20one-sided%20police%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20has%20also%20said%20that%20after%20he%20received%20a%20call%20from%20local%20police%2C%20he%20reached%20the%20petrol%20pump%2C%20spoke%20to%20its%20owner%20and%20%26quot%3Bsettled%26quot%3B%20the%20matter.%20But%20later%20he%20learnt%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bimplicated%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20case%20by%20the%20police%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20the%20complainant%2C%20has%20alleged%20that%20Anas%20arrived%20there%20in%20his%20car%20and%20asked%20the%20salesman%20to%20refuel%20his%20car%20first.%20%26quot%3BHe%20then%20started%20beating%20the%20salesman%20and%20threatened%20that%20he%20was%20the%20MLA's%20son.%20He%20took%20out%20an%20iron%20rod%20from%20the%20car%20and%20started%20hitting%20around.%20He%20also%20broke%20the%20card%20machine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FIR%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20protect%20the%20salesman%2C%20other%20petrol%20pump%20employees%20got%20involved%20in%20the%20scuffle.%20The%20police%20were%20called%20in.%20But%20he%20fled%20the%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20adds%20that%20Anas%20returned%20later%20to%20the%20fuel%20pump%20and%20threatened%20to%20thrash%20all%20the%20employees%20there.%20%26quot%3BHe%20then%20called%20his%20father%20who%20arrived%20there%20in%20a%20convoy%20of%20two%20cars%20and%20threatened%20the%20pump%20manager%20by%20saying%20that%20he%20(manager)%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20if%20he%20(Khan)%20starts%20beating%20him%20and%20the%20workers.%20The%20MLA%20then%20spoke%20to%20the%20pump%20owner%20over%20the%20phone%20and%20told%20him%20that%20this%20pump%20falls%20in%20our%20area%20and%20if%20you%20are%20here%20to%20do%20business%2C%20then%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complainant%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20several%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20sections%2C%20including%20those%20related%20to%20voluntarily%20causing%20hurt%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%20and%20mischief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20two-time%20MLA%20from%20Okhla%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20was%20declared%20a%20'bad%20character'%20by%20Delhi%20Police%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20told%20AAP%20MLAs%20that%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20to%20topple%20the%20party's%20governments%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20after%20his%20arrest%20on%20March%2021%2C%20but%20the%20plan%20did%20not%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20become%20more%20united%20after%20his%20arrest.%20%26quot%3BThey%20had%20a%20plan%20that%20they%20will%20arrest%20me%2C%20break%20the%20party%2C%20topple%20the%20government%20in%20Delhi%20and%20then%20in%20Punjab%20also.%20After%20arrest%2C%20their%20plan%20failed.%20You%20all%20did%20not%20break%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20national%20convener%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20a%20money-laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20now-scrapped%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20Friday%20granted%20him%20interim%20bail%20so%20that%20he%20can%20campaign%20for%20the%20ongoin