ced%20by%20their%20performance%20in%202019.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20phase%20marks%20the%20conclusion%20of%20polling%20in%20the%20southern%20region%20of%20India%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Findia-decides%2Fa-look-at-key-contests-in-phase-4-783642%5C%22%3ETelangana%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnever-considered-jagan-reddy-an-ally-but-pm-modi-on-andhra-tie-up-5639077%5C%22%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20casting%20their%20votes%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20is%20also%20conducting%20simultaneous%20polls%20for%20assembly%20as%20well%20as%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Ten%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%2C%20including%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(25)%2C%20Bihar%20(5)%2C%20Jharkhand%20(4)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(8)%2C%20Maharashtra%20(11)%2C%20Odisha%20(4)%2C%20Telangana%20(17)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(13)%2C%20West%20Bengal%20(8)%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(1)%2C%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20May%2013%20elections.%20Notably%2C%2042%20out%20of%20the%2096%20seats%20(44%25)%20are%20spread%20across%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20secured%2042%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20six%2C%20and%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20(YSRCP)%2022.%20The%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20clinched%2049%20seats%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20eight%2C%20and%20non-aligned%20regional%20parties%20like%20the%20YSRCP%2C%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%2C%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20secured%2039%20seats%20collectively.%20While%20the%20NDA%20attained%20a%2053%25%20vote%20share%20for%20the%20seats%20it%20won%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20secured%2045%25%2C%20and%20non-aligned%20parties%20garnered%2048%25.%20In%20terms%20of%20victory%20margins%2C%20the%20NDA%20averaged%2017%25%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%C2%A0%208%25%2C%20and%20non-aligned%20parties%2011%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20contesting%2070%20seats%20in%20this%20phase%2C%20with%20its%20allies%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20contesting%2017%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20three%2C%20and%20Jana%20Sena%20two.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20contesting%2061%20seats%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2019%2C%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Sena%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20four%20seats%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENon-Aligned%20Parties%20Are%20Key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20victory%20margins%2C%20the%20BJP%20secured%2014%20seats%20in%20close%20contests%20with%20less%20than%2010%25%20margin%2C%20while%20it%20won%2028%20seats%20by%20a%20substantial%20margin%20of%20more%20than%2010%25.%20However%2C%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20witnessed%20lower%20strike%20rates%20compared%20to%20their%20overall%20strike%20rates%20in%20that%20year%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20registering%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2047%25%20versus%2069%25%20overall%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%207%25%20compared%20to%2012%25%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-aligned%20parties%20secured%2039%20seats%20in%20this%20phase%2C%20with%20the%20YSRCP%20(22)%2C%20the%20BJD%20(2)%2C%20the%20TMC%20(4)%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20or%20BRS%20(9)%2C%20and%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%2C%20or%20AIMIM%20(2)%20seats.%20Although%20the%20TMC%20claims%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20its%20absence%20from%20any%20seat%20arrangement%20with%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal%20categorises%20it%20as%20non-aligned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20data-ved%3D%5C%222ahUKEwjUiu-axYeGAxWHcWwGHTnuAEQQFnoECBQQAQ%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-polls-can-telangana-help-bjp-boost-its-tally-in-south-india-5630604%5C%22%20ping%3D%5C%22%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26amp%3Bsource%3Dweb%26amp%3Brct%3Dj%26amp%3Bopi%3D89978449%26amp%3Burl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-polls-can-telangana-help-bjp-boost-its-tally-in-south-india-5630604%26amp%3Bved%3D2ahUKEwjUiu-axYeGAxWHcWwGHTnuAEQQFnoECBQQAQ%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%3A%20Can%20Telangana%20Boost%20BJP's%20Tally%20In%20South%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20these%20parties%20-%20the%20YSRCP%2C%20the%20BJD%2C%20and%20the%20BRS%20-%20have%20supported%20the%20BJP%20in%20passing%20key%20bills%20in%20Parliament%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Upper%20House%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20lacks%20a%20majority.%20Before%20polling%20commenced%2C%20there%20was%20significant%20speculation%20about%20a%20possible%20BJP-BJD%20tie-up%20in%20Odisha.%20However%2C%20such%20an%20alliance%20could%20have%20bolstered%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20state%2C%20potentially%20making%20it%20the%20primary%20opposition.%20Thus%2C%20the%20idea%20was%20abandoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20BJD%20are%20the%20primary%20contenders%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Congress%20alleges%20there's%20an%20under-the-table%20deal%20between%20the%20two.%20Even%20if%20the%20BJP%20fails%20to%20breach%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20stronghold%2C%20the%20BJD%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20supporting%20the%20NDA%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20given%20the%20Congress's%20weak%20position%20in%20winning%20seats.%20Naveen's%20popularity%20and%20Odia%20identity%20work%20in%20his%20favour%2C%20minimising%20the%20possibility%20of%20significant%20split%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWin-Win%20For%20BJP%20In%20Odisha%2C%20Andhra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20sought%20alliances%2C%20but%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20YSRCP%20remained%20a%20steadfast%20supporter.%20The%20YSRCP%20enjoys%20robust%20minority%20support%2C%20and%20with%20Congress%20elevating%20Jagan's%20sister%20Sharmila%20as%20the%20state%20unit%20president%2C%20any%20alignment%20with%20BJP%20could%20have%20jeopardised%20this%20voter%20bloc%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20forming%20an%20alliance%20with%20former%20partner%20TDP%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20to%20secure%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20seats%20for%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20While%20the%20TDP%20relies%20on%20issues%20of%20unemployment%20and%20development%2C%20the%20YSRCP%20focuses%20on%20women%20and%20beneficiaries.%20Similar%20to%20Odisha%2C%20the%20BJP's%20prospects%20rest%20on%20the%20TDP's%20performance.%20Even%20if%20the%20TDP%20falters%20and%20the%20YSRCP%20succeeds%2C%20Jagan%20is%20likely%20to%20maintain%20his%20anti-Congress%20stance%2C%20ensuring%20a%20win-win%20scenario%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20both%20Odisha%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Failure%20to%20do%20so%20may%20hamper%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fname-all-districts-of-odisha-pm-modi-dare-to-naveen-patnaik-5639666%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BName%20All%20Districts%20Of%20Odisha%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Dare%20To%20Naveen%20Patnaik%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20polarise%20the%20contest%2C%20making%20it%20a%20two-way%20battle%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20leveraging%20the%20weakening%20of%20the%20BRS%20due%20to%20the%20departure%20of%20leaders%20and%20the%20arrest%20of%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao's%20daughter%2C%20Kavitha.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Congress%20seeks%20to%20solidify%20its%20gains%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20polls%2C%20capitalising%20on%20its%20track%20record%20of%20fulfilling%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVarious%20Possibilities%20In%20Other%20States%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftaking-to-skies-for-democracy-polling-staff-airdropped-in-jharkhands-naxal-hit-singhbhum-5641543%5C%22%3EJharkhand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%2