d%20Parents%20For%20Giving%20Birth%20Without%20Permission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20from%20New%20Jersey%2C%20United%20States%2C%20claimed%20that%20she%20sued%20her%20parents%20for%20giving%20birth%20to%20her%20without%20her%20consent%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indy100.com%2Ftiktok%2Fwoman-sues-parents-birth-tiktok-2668234400%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent's%20Indy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20joked%20that%20%26quot%3Bthey%20didn't%20try%20to%20contact%20me%20in%20anyway%20before%20I%20was%20born%20to%20see%20if%20I%20actually%20wanted%20to%20be%20here.%26quot%3B%20Kass%20Theaz%2C%20the%20TikToker%20mentions%20in%20her%20bio%20that%20her%20account%20is%20%26quot%3Bsatire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Theaz%20also%20explained%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsoCYNFAnN-%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20reason%20why%20she%20had%20children%20of%20her%20own%20even%20though%20she%20had%20sued%20her%20parents%20for%20having%20her%20against%20her%20will.%20The%20content%20creator%20stated%20that%20since%20she%20had%20adopted%20her%20children%2C%20she%20had%20no%20role%20in%20conceiving%20them%20without%20their%20consent.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20my%20fault%20that%20they're%20here.%20if%20you%20are%20pregnant%20right%20now%20you%20need%20to%20go%20you%20need%20to%20hire%20a%20psychic%20medium%20and%20ask%20if%20they%20actually%20wanna%20be%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20my%20parents%20that%20I%20sued.%20They%20contributed%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20conceiving%20me%2C%20and%20my%20mother%20that%20raised%20me%2C%20she%20gave%20birth%20to%20me.%20And%20that's%20why%20I%20sued%20them%2C%20because%20I%20did%20not%20consent%20to%20being%20here%2C%20like%2C%20I%20was%20unaware%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20have%20to%20grow%20up%20and%20get%20a%20job%20to%20support%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Theaz%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F05%2F25%2Fi-sued-my-parents-for-having-me-without-my-permission-now-i-have-kids%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%20in%20the%20clip%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20just%20didn't%20consent%20to%20that.%20They%20didn't%20try%20to%20contact%20me%20in%20any%20way%20before%20I%20was%20born%20to%20see%20if%20I%20actually%20wanted%20to%20be%20here%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20I%20sued%20them.%20Otherwise%2C%20they%20will%20sue%20you%20because%20I'm%20making%20that%20my%20life%20mission%20to%20teach%20children%20to%20sue%20their%20parents%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TikTok%20star%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20different%20when%20you%20adopt%20because%20it's%20not%20my%20fault%20that%20they're%20here.%20I'm%20just%20trying%20to%20be%20a%20good%20person%20and%20help%20them%20out.%20You%20know%20what%20I%20mean%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnaware%20that%20Ms%20Theaz's%20account%20was%20satire%2C%20some%20viewers%20expressed%20confusion%2C%20with%20one%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20real%3F%26quot%3B%20Comments%20like%20%26quot%3Byou%20need%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bplease%20tell%20me%20you're%20joking%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnow%20they're%20teaching%20children%20to%20sue%20their%20parents%20for%20money%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20grow%20up%20and%20work%3F%26quot%3B%20were%20made%20by%20other%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20my%20children%20would%20sue%20me.%20Because%20I%20in%20return%20would%20sue%20them%20for%20all%20the%20money%20I%20had%20to%20put%20out%20over%20the%20years.%20Lol%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20it%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20your%20account%20says%20Satire%20Account%20and%20everybody's%20asking%20if%20your%20joking%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20add