%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349510%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Situated%20in%20Kalimpong%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Kabir%20Pradhan%20and%20Ahana%20Gurung's%20homestay%20is%20made%20of%20mud%20and%20bamboo.%20It's%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20couple's%20love%20for%20their%20hometown%20and%20commitment%20to%20sustainable%20living.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Why%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Brilliant%20Women%20Return%20to%20Work%20After%20Motherhood%3F%E2%80%99%3A%20Startup%20Finding%20Jobs%20for%20New%20Moms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20landmark%20ruling%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20declared%20that%20two-year%20childcare%20leave%20%E2%80%94%20apart%20from%20maternity%20leave%20of%20180%20days%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20constitutional%20mandate%20for%20women%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20%E2%80%94%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20%E2%80%94%20emphasised%20that%20denying%20such%20leave%20forces%20women%20to%20resign.%20%E2%80%9CParticipation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20workforce%20is%20not%20a%20privilege%20but%20a%20constitutional%20mandate.%20Child%20care%20leave%20subserves%20an%20important%20constitutional%20objective%20to%20make%20women%20be%20part%20of%20the%20workforce.%20Otherwise%2C%20mothers%20will%20be%20left%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs%20to%20look%20after%20their%20children%20in%20critical%20phases%20of%20their%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20concealed%20that%20Indian%20women%20have%20long%20been%20burdened%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98motherhood%20penalty%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatistically%20speaking%2C%2073%20percent%20of%20Indian%20women%20leave%20their%20jobs%20after%20giving%20birth%3B%2050%20percent%20leave%20their%20jobs%20to%20take%20care%20of%20their%