0puri%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20mine%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20we%20here%20in%20India%20take%20for%20granted%20%E2%80%94%20and%20enjoy%20it%2C%20was%20amazing.%20At%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20challenge%2C%20I%20remember%20being%20sceptical%20about%20whether%20I%20should%20make%20pani%20puri%20or%20not%2C%20but%20then%20I%20figured%20that%20one%20cannot%20speak%20of%20street%20food%20in%20India%20without%20mentioning%20the%20pani%20puri%2C%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20having%20Jamie%20Oliver%20love%20it%20was%20all%20the%20validation%20she%20needed!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsumeet-saigal-1-1715177462.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sumeet's%20pani%20puri%20won%20hearts%20and%20palettes%20in%20the%20MasterChef%20kitchen%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsumeet-saigal-1-1715177462.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsumeet-saigal-1-1715177462-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsumeet-saigal-1-1715177462-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsumeet-saigal-1-1715177462-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsumeet-saigal-1-1715177462-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349374%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESumeet%E2%80%99s%20pani%20puri%20won%20hearts%20and%20palettes%20in%20the%20MasterChef%20kitchen%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaigal%20sees%20these%20moments%20as%20a%20nod%20to%20her%20efforts%20to%20bring%20Indian%20food%20to%20a%20global%20stage.%20She%20enjoys%20feeding%20others%2C%20a%20habit%20she%20borrowed%20from%20watching%20her%20parents%20entertain%20guests%20and%20host%20parties%20in%20their%20Bengaluru%20home.%20Her%20memories%20of%20food%20are%20anecdotal%2C%20as%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20fascinating%20to%20watch%20a%20detailed%20menu%20coming%20to%20life%20and%20watching%20everyone%2C%20not%20just%20my%20mother%2C%20but%20also%20my%20father%20be%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdd%20to%20these%20experiences%20the%20fact%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347983%2Fdosa-origin-story-bengaluru-butter-masala-dosa-history-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20central%20to%20their%20lives%2C%20gratis%20her%20Punjabi%20genes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99d%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20while%20having%20our%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(an%20Indian%20flatbread)%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20already%20be%20planning%20our%20lunch%20menu.%20During%20lunch%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20plan%20for%20evening%20snacks%20and%20while%20having%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewe%E2%80%99d%20discuss%20dinner%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Sundays%2C%20the%20menu%20was%20non-negotiable.%20The%20spot%20on%20the%20table%20was%20reserved%20for%20%3Cem%3Emutton%20biryani%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20comprising%20meat%20cooked%20in%20spices%2C%20herbs%20and%20yoghurt%2C%20served%20with%20rice).%20And%20as%20the%20family%20gathered%20to%20feast%2C%20bonds%20were%20formed%2C%20laughs%20were%20shared%2C%20jokes%20were%20cracked%2C%20and%20memories%20were%20etched%20onto%20a%20young%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instag