e-masala-powder-spice-mix-at-home-recipes-mdh-everest-sambar-biryani-pav-bhaji-masala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflavouring%20condiments%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20instead%20powerful%20symbols%20of%20Indian%20gastronomy%3B%20the%20ingredients%20that%20render%20Indian%20food%20its%20distinct%20taste.%20%E2%80%9CSpices%20are%20our%20superpower%2C%20something%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20double%20guess.%20Like%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20rainbow%2C%20each%20spice%20is%20beautiful%20in%20its%20own%20right.%20I%20see%20them%20like%20music%20notes.%20You%20can%20adjust%20the%20levels%20but%20still%20end%20up%20with%20a%20beautiful%20rendition%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20apt%20example%20of%20this%20metaphor%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20dabba%3C%2Fem%3E%20(spice%20box)%20in%20Indian%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20each%20have%20the%20same%20dabba%20but%20a%20curry%20in%20my%20house%20won%E2%80%99t%20resemble%20the%20one%20in%20yours.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20is%20amazing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20further%20pay%20homage%20to%20Indian%20spices%2C%20Saigal%20shares%20a%20dream%20she%20has%20long%20since%20harboured%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Sauce%20Boss%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20will%20make%20sauces%20easily%20available%20and%20accessible%20for%20people%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20experiences%20that%20influenced%20this%20dream%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20my%20trips%20to%20India%2C%20I%20see%20a%20huge%20variety.%20A%20curry%20in%20North%20India%20is%20different%20from%20one%20in%20South%20India%3B%20a%20curry%20in%20Kolkata%20is%20different%20from%20one%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20on%20the%20western%20coast.%20While%20we%20recognise%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22htt