0stands%20proud%20in%20her%20white%20apron%20emblazoned%20with%20her%20name%2C%20Saigal%20sees%20it%20as%20a%20realisation%20of%20a%20long-time%20dream.%20%E2%80%9CI%20recall%20watching%20MasterChef%20Australia%20for%20the%20first%20time%20with%20my%20twins%20years%20ago.%20We%E2%80%99d%20watch%20excitedly%20as%20contestants%20planned%20their%20dishes%20and%20came%20up%20with%20amazing%20stuff.%20My%20kids%20would%20go%20%E2%80%98Okay%20mom%2C%20now%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20a%20challenge.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20got%20to%20make%20something%20using%20what%E2%80%99s%20there%20in%20the%20fridge!%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20how%20it%20started.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20dish%20Saigal%20prepares%20has%20a%20sensory%20richness%20to%20it%20%E2%80%94%20sight%2C%20smell%20and%20taste%20compete%20to%20thrill%20the%20judges.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20I%20would%20watch%20the%20show%20with%20my%20twins%2C%20I%20always%20found%20it%20to%20be%20so%20wholesome%3B%20a%20great%20bonding%20experience%3B%20something%20to%20come%20home%20to.%20I%20would%20watch%20in%20awe%20as%20the%20judges%20gave%20feedback%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309089%2Fhow-to-start-business-engineer-quits-job-to-start-homecooked-food-startup-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20cooks%20%3C%2Fa%3Edished%20out%20incredible%20things%2C%20and%20pushed%20the%20boundaries%20of%20their%20skills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20has%20watched%20Saigal%20grow%20from%20strength%20to%20strength%20and%20she%20credits%20its%20challenges%20for%20boosting%20her%20creativity%20and%20quick%20thinking.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20expressions%20of%20surprise%20you%20see%20are%20all%20real%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20gratitude%20colours%20her%20emotional%20palette%20as%20she%20looks%20back%20on%20her%20journey.%20But%20it%20is%20intriguing%20how%20it%20all%20transpired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EShe%20reveals%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20day%20while%20watching%20the%20show%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20screen%20and%20said%20%E2%80%98That%20%5Bthe%20MasterChef%20kitchen%5D%20is%20where%20I%20want%20to%20be.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20up%20your%20mind%20and%20the%20entire%20universe%20will%20conspire%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715179195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349245%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sumeet%20Saigal%2C%20a%20contestant%20on%20MasterChef%20Australia%2C%20was%20influenced%20by%20her%20Punjabi%20family's%20culinary%20legacy.%20Here's%20her%20journey%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Australia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20Farmers%20Earn%20More%20By%20Selling%20Kinnaur%E2%80%99s%20Famous%20%E2%80%98Black%20Gold%E2%80%99%20Directly%20to%20Consumers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20the%20eastern%20part%20of%20the%20Sutlej%20River%20in%20the%20Kinnaur%20district%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Bhaba%20is%20a%20pristine%20valley%20surrounded%20by%20snow-clad%20peaks%2C%20lush%20valleys%20full%20of%20apple%20orchards%2C%20and%20tall%20pine%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20irresistible%20beauty%2C%20tranquil%20environment%2C%20and%20rocky%20mountainscape%20attract%20thousands%20of%20tourists%20every%20year.%20However%2C%20one%20of%20its%20residents%2C%20Ashish%20Negi%2C%20was%20deprived%20of%20its%20charm%20when%20he%20moved%20out%20for%20work%20in%20crowded%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20admired%20our%20tribal%20ways%20of%20living%20%E2%80%94%20quaint%20village%20setting%2C%20simplicity%20of%20people%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20traditions%20that%20have%20been%20followed%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%20My%20village%20in%20Kinnaur%20is%20a%20gem%20of%20a%20mountain%20place.%20We%20have%20a%20very%20small%20population%20and%20the%20pollution%20level%20is%20almost%20zero%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashish%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Huri%20village%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20strong%20longing%2C%20he%20would%20be%20able%20to%20come%20back%20to%20his%20hometown%20only%20once%20a%20year.%20Eventually%2C%20in%202011%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20four-year-long%20career%20in%20mechanical%20engineering%20to%20move%20to%20his%20village%20permanently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20desire%20to%20reconnect%20with%20his%20roots%2C%20Ashish%20yearned%20to%20look%20after%20his%20ancestral%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F58210%2Ffruit-orchard-destinations-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapple%20orchards%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20were%20lying%20unattended.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20Kinnaur%20is%20known%20worldwide%20for%20its%20apples%2C%20our%20orchards%20were%20abandoned%20as%20there%20were%20no%20young%20members%20in%20my%20family%20to%20look%20after%20them.%20The%20land%20was%20losing%20its%20richness%20and%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20bear%20that.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20prime%20reasons%20why%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-2-1715174392.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashish%20adds%20that