.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20has%20a%20high%20value.%20And%20these%20can%20be%20grown%20only%20in%20our%20region%20given%20our%20climatic%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Ashish%20aims%20to%20commercialise%20value-added%20products%20of%20these%20apples%20to%20further%20the%20income%20of%20regional%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20aim%20to%20process%20apples%20into%20jams%2C%20vinegar%2C%20juices%2C%20and%20healthy%20dried%20apple%20chips.%20Our%20processing%20unit%20will%20be%20operational%20from%20September%20onwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reveals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20city%20life%2C%20Ashish%20finds%20contentment%20in%20rural%20farm%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20enjoy%20my%20field%20of%20work%20as%20I%20get%20to%20meet%20real%20India%20%E2%80%93%20its%20small%20farmers.%20With%20my%20work%2C%20I%20see%20improvements%20in%20front%20of%20me%20every%20day.%20These%20farmers%20were%20once%20in%20distress%20and%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20middlemen.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20help%20them%20even%20on%20a%20very%20basic%20level%20is%20so%20fulfilling.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20helping%20a%20person%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20helping%20the%20whole%20family%20and%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Ashish%20Negi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715177558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349336%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashish%20Negi%20left%20his%20engineering%20career%20to%20revive%20ancestral%20apple%20orchards%20in%20Kinnaur.%20He%20now%20runs%20'Kayang'%20to%20empower%20local%20farmers%20by%20directly%20supplying%20Kinnauri%20apples%20to%20customers%2C%20eliminating%20middlemen%20and%20other%20exploitative%20market%20practices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20Microgreens%20At%20Home%3F%20Entrepreneur%20Sells%2050%20kg%2FMonth%2C%20Shares%20Tips%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aditi%20Mali%2C%20an%20urban%20farmer%20and%20visiting%20professor%20at%20Ahmedabad%20College%2C%20decided%20to%20connect%20her%20students%20to%20farming%20by%20making%20it%20practical%2C%20she%20faced%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20ask%20my%20students%20to%20adopt%20a%20plant%20and%20grow%20it%2C%20but%20by%20the%20time%20the%20course%20ended%2C%20the%20plant%20had%20only%20grown%20a%20little%20bit.%20Since%20it%20takes%20longer%20for%20a%20fruit%20or%20vegetable%20to%20grow%2C%20the%20activity%20was%20not%20as%20fruitful%20as%20I%20hoped%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20she%20discovered%20an%20alternative%3A%20growing%20microgreens.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20not%20aware%20that%20what%20began%20as%20a%20way%20to%20make%20farming%20more%20engaging%20for%20her%20students%20would%20later%20become%20a%20career%20path%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMicrogreen%20plants%20require%20less%20time%20to%20grow%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20an%20excellent%20option%20for%20my%20students%20to%20cultivate.%20However%2C%20as%20I%20began%20to%20explore%20them%20further%2C%20I%20realised%20they%20are%20nutrient-dense%20and%20are%20considered%20a%20superfood%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Aditi%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Mali%20Greens%2C%20a%20business%20that%20offers%20over%2018%20different%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%20to%20more%20than%20900%20customers%20across%20the%20city.%20We%20talked%20to%20her%20extensively%20about%20the%20intricacies%20of%20running%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304873%2Fkerala-man-grows-microgreens-superfood-at-home-earns-lakh