rs%20onboard%20the%20boat%20clinic%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848-500x282.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848-768x433.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848-150x85.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPatients%20across%2030%20islands%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%20are%20treated%20by%20the%20doctors%20onboard%20the%20boat%20clinic%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wohab%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20would%20soon%20learn%2C%20the%20man%20was%20Grandjean%20Gaston%2C%20a%20nurse%20from%20Switzerland.%20%E2%80%9CBrother%20Gaston%20had%20been%20battling%20a%20heart%20condition%20and%20had%20decided%20to%20dedicate%20his%20life%20to%20the%20poor%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wohab%20explains.%20He%20wanted%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20that%20year%2C%20inspired%20by%20Gaston%E2%80%99s%20story%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20recalibrate%20their%20plans%3B%20and%20moved%20back%20to%20their%20hometown%20in%20Bhangar%2C%20South%2024%20Parganas.%20The%20goal%20of%20this%20move%20was%20simple%3A%20Spot%20areas%20where%20their%20communities%20lacked%20resources%20and%20bridge%20those%20gaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20flood%20waters%20began%20to%20recede%2C%20they%20left%20behind%20many%20challenges%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20chill%20in%20the%20air%20and%20the%20bacteria%20breeding%20in%20the%20murky%20waters%20had%20only%20added%20to%20the%20existing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331526%2Fpune-startup-innovates-ai-based-technology-screen-tuberculosis-within-seconds-innovation-in-healthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattle%20against%20tuberculosis%3C%2Fa%3E%20(TB)%20that%20the%20community%20was%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20dying%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wohab%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20often%20started%20with%20a%20cough%20and%20before%20the%20person%20knew%20it%2C%20they%20were%20detected%20with%20TB.%20As%20we%20spoke%20to%20people%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20almost%2050%20percent%20of%20people%20with%20chest%20problems%20did%20not%20go%20for%20a%20checkup%20until%20they%20started%20vomiting%20blood.%20And%20once%20they%20reached%20this%20stage%2C%20it%20was%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20too%20late.%20We%20also%20found%20that%20there%20were%20only%20three%20doctors%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%20at%20that%20time%20and%20more%20than%20three%20lakh%20patients.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20to%20help.%20They%20had%20heard%20about%20doctors%20in%20Kolkata%20who%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259846%2Fdoctors-couple-covid-relief-free-medicine-collection-underprivileged-shell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributing%20medicines%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20free.%20%E2%80%9CSabitri%20and%20I%20started%20making%20trips%20to%20these%20clinics%20to%20collect%20the%20medicine%20samples%20which%20we%20distributed%20in%20a%20small%20room%20that%20a%20tea%20shop%20owner%20had%20lent%20to%20us.%20Through%20the%20weeks%2C%20people%20from%20across%20Sundarban%20islands%20would%20come%20to%20get%20an%20antidote%20to%20tuberculosis%2C%20c