arees%20would%20be%20sold.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20they%20would%20return%20to%20us%20after%20a%20month%20or%20so%20and%20dump%20all%20the%20unsold%20sarees.%20The%20onus%20to%20sell%20these%20would%20fall%20on%20us.%20But%20with%20Deeva%2C%20we%20get%20orders%20only%20after%20the%20consumer%20has%20placed%20an%20order%2C%20and%20we%20get%20payments%20in%207%20to%2010%20days.%20Here%2C%20my%20income%20has%20also%20increased%20by%2025%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20to%20make%20Deeva%20a%20big%20brand%2C%20Ankush%20wanted%20to%20appear%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%20Even%20though%20he%20could%20not%20make%20it%20to%20season%202%2C%20he%20made%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98sharks%E2%80%99%20in%20season%203.%20The%20impact%20of%20the%20episode%20was%20so%20enormous%20that%20he%20observed%20a%20boost%20of%20six%20times%20in%20his%20business%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooted%20in%20his%20village%2C%20Ankush%20now%20aims%20to%20make%20a%20business%20of%20Rs%20150%20crore%2C%20enter%20into%20export%20in%20at%20least%2010%20countries%2C%20and%20open%20offline%20stores%20in%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20feel%20I%20have%20achieved%20very%20big.%20It%20was%20through%20my%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20that%20we%20started%20getting%20meals%20three%20times%20a%20day.%20My%20parents%20worked%20hard%20so%20that%20we%20could%20wear%20decent%20clothes.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20give%20whatever%20best%20life%20I%20can%20to%20my%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20I%20gifted%20a%20seven-seater%20car%20to%20my%20father.%20Currently%2C%20we%20are%20building%20our%20dream%20house%20with%20a%20helipad%20and%20rooftop%20swimming%20pool%20in%20Himachal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20these%20are%20materialistic%20things%2C%20having%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebada%20ghar%2C%20badi%20gaadi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(big%20house%2C%20big%20car)%20are%20dreams%20of%20a%20lower-middle%20income%20family.%20In%20eight%20months%2C%20I%20will%20move%20to%20our%20new%20home%20with%20my%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Ankush%20Barjata.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714745043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ankush%20Barjata%20founded%20an%20online%20saree%20platform%20named%20'Deeva'%20from%20a%20small%20Himachal%20village.%20His%20journey%2C%20rooted%20in%20his%20family's%20clothing%20legacy%2C%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20vision%20to%20provide%20a%20better%20life%20for%20his%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20An%20Architect%20is%20Using%20Stationery%20to%20Prevent%209000%20Kg%20Cotton%20Waste%20From%20Reaching%20Landfills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERashi%20Agarwal%E2%80%99s%20final%20year%20of%20college%20was%20incredibly%20enriching.%20She%20embarked%20on%20a%20nationwide%20journey%20to%20explore%20traditional%20art%20and%20craft%20forms%2C%20all%20for%20her%20thesis.%20From%20Delhi%20to%20Jaipur%2C%20Kutch%20to%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20Puducherry%20to%20Pune%2C%20she%20sought%20out%20artisans%2C%20absorbing%20their%20knowledge%20and%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20diversity%20of%20art%20forms%20she%20encountered%2C%20there%20was%20a%20unifying%20thread%20among%20them%20all%20%E2%80%94%20the%20dwindling%20demand%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316686%2Fartist-helps-women-tamil-nadu-earn-upcycles-coconut-shells-into-eco-friendly-goods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandcrafted%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20society%20gravitated%20toward%20machine-printed%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20could%20this%2025-year-old%20find%20a%20way%20to%20provide%20a%20livelihood%20to%20these%20artisans%3F%20This%20question%20gnawed%20at%20the%20Surat%20resident%20even%20after%20she%20returned%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20she%20began%20painting%20the%20cover%20pages%20of%20diaries%2C%20which%20were%20highly%20appreciated%20by%20her%20friends%20and%20family.%20Since%20most%20of%20the%20artisans%20she%20visited%20worked%20in%20the%20paper%20industry%2C%20she%20wondered%20if%20she%20could%20turn%20her%20love%20for%20drawing%20and%20painting%20into%20a%20business%20that%20would%20provide%20employment%20to%20people%20who%20worked%20by%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wanted%20to%20revolutionise%20the%20space%20by%20making%20these%20age-old%20practices%20of%20handmade%20products%20appealing%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20consumers%20and%20bringing%20them%20back%20into%20trend.%20With%20this%20thought%20in%20mind%2C%20Rashi%20started%20%E2%80%98Roohani%20Rang%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20handmade%20stationery%20business%20that%20sells%20sustainable%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20the%20venture%20stand%20apart%20is%20that%20the%20products%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20diaries%2C%20planners%2C%20calendars%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20are%20made%20out%20of%20cotton%20waste.%20So%20far%2C%20Rashi%20has%20sold%20over%2015%2C000%20planners%20and%20employed%20over%2050%20artisans%2C%20while%20recycling%209%2C732%20kg%20of%20cotton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20trees%20were%20harmed%20in%20making%20this%20paper%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20final%20year%20of%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20at%20the%20Raman%20Bhakta%20School%20of%20Architecture%20in%20Surat%2C%20Rashi%20decided%20to%20venture%20into%20business.%20The%20catch%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%202020%2C%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20COVID-19%20was%20wreaking%20havoc%20across%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20then%20student%20had%20just%20Rs%205%2C000%20to